== 製作 ==
2018年7月，宣佈[[林-曼努爾·米蘭達|林-曼努爾·米蘭達]]執導一部改編自舞台劇的電影，該片將是他的導演處女作，並由{{le|史蒂文·萊文森|Steven Levenson}}撰寫劇本，[[Imagine_Entertainment|Imagine Entertainment]]製作<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|url=https://deadline.com/2018/07/lin-manuel-miranda-directing-debut-tick-tick-boom-hamilton-jonathan-larson-steven-levenson-imagine-entertainment-musical-movie-1202429317/|title=Imagine Sets Lin-Manuel Miranda’s Helming Debut: ‘Rent’ Creator Jonathan -Larson’s ‘Tick, Tick…Boom!’; ‘Evan Hansen’s Steven Levenson Scripting|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2018-07-19|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2018-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719193155/https://deadline.com/2018/07/lin-manuel-miranda-directing-debut-tick-tick-boom-hamilton-jonathan-larson-steven-levenson-imagine-entertainment-musical-movie-1202429317/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年6月，[[Netflix|Netflix]]收購了該片的發行權，而[[安德魯·加菲爾德|安德魯·加菲爾德]]是主角的首要人選<ref>{{cite web|last=Kroll|first=Justin|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/netflix-tick-tick-boom-lin-manuel-miranda-andrew-garfield-1203246569/|title=Netflix Lands Lin-Manuel Miranda’s ‘Tick, Tick… Boom!’ (EXCLUSIVE)|publisher=[[Variety|Variety]]|date=2019-06-19|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403032832/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/netflix-tick-tick-boom-lin-manuel-miranda-andrew-garfield-1203246569/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月，確認加菲爾-德出演電影<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/andrew-garfield-lin-manuel-miranda-rent-playwright-jonathan-larson-tick-tick-boom-netflix-1202772429/|title=Andrew Garfield To Star In Lin-Manuel Miranda Netflix Adaptation of ‘Rent’ Playwright Jonathan Larson’s ‘tick, tick…BOOM!’|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-10-30|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030030853/https://deadline.com/2019/10/andrew-garfield-lin-manuel-miranda-rent-playwright-jonathan-larson-tick-tick-boom-netflix-1202772429/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月，宣佈[[雅莉珊卓·希普|雅莉珊卓·希普]]、[[凡妮莎·哈金斯|凡妮莎·哈金斯]]和{{le|羅賓·德·哈蘇|Robin de Jesús}}加盟劇組<ref>{{cite web|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/alexandra-shipp-andrew-garfield-tick-tick-boom-vanessa-hudgens-robin-de-jesus-netflix-film-1202772707/|title=Alexandra Shipp Joins Andrew Garfield In ‘tick, tick…BOOM!’; Vanessa Hudgens & Robin de Jesus Also Cast In Netflix Adaptation|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-11-04|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111203410/https://deadline.com/2019/11/alexandra-shipp-andrew-garfield-tick-tick-boom-vanessa-hudgens-robin-de-jesus-netflix-film-1202772707/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年1月，宣佈{{le|約書亞·亨利|Joshua Henry}}、{{le|茱蒂絲·萊特|Judith Light}}和[[布萊德利·惠特福德|布萊德利·惠特福德]]加盟劇組<ref>{{cite web|last=Donnelly|first=Matt|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/lin-manuel-mirandas-tick-tick-boom-adds-joshua-henry-judith-light-bradley-whitford-exclusive-1203483884/|title=Lin-Manuel Miranda’s ‘Tick, Tick… Boom!’ Adds Joshua Henry, Judith Light, Bradley Whitford (EXCLUSIVE)|publisher=[[Variety|Variety]]|date=2020-01-28|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822113814/https://variety.com/2020/film/news/lin-manuel-mirandas-tick-tick-boom-adds-joshua-henry-judith-light-bradley-whitford-exclusive-1203483884/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Sinha-Roy|first=Piya|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/vanessa-hudgens-alexandra-shipp-join-lin-manuel-mirandas-tick-tickboom-1252310|title=Vanessa Hudgens, Alexandra Shipp, Robin de Jesus Join Andrew Garfield in Lin-Manuel Miranda's 'tick, tick...BOOM!'|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2019-11-04|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117025606/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/vanessa-hudgens-alexandra-shipp-join-lin-manuel-mirandas-tick-tickboom-1252310|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2020年3月3日在[[紐約市|紐約市]]開始進行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Lin-Manuel-Miranda-Shares-Photo-From-First-Day-of-Filming-TICK-TICKBOOM-20200303|title=Lin-Manuel Miranda Shares Photo From First Day of Filming TICK, TICK...BOOM!|publisher=Broadway World|date=2020-03-03|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200303154947/https://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Lin-Manuel-Miranda-Shares-Photo-From-First-Day-of-Filming-TICK-TICKBOOM-20200303|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Suri|first=Sameer|url=https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-8075159/Andrew-Garfield-reviews-lines-director-Lin-Manuel-Miranda-shoots-Tick-Tick-Boom.html|title=Andrew Garfield fights the sniffles as he joins director Lin-Manuel Miranda on set of new film Tick, Tick... Boom|publisher=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|date=2020-03-05|accessdate=2020-10-21|archive-date=2020-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621143112/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-8075159/Andrew-Garfield-reviews-lines-director-Lin-Manuel-Miranda-shoots-Tick-Tick-Boom.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年4月，受[[2019冠狀病毒病疫情|2019冠狀病毒病疫情]]影響，本片暫停拍攝<ref>{{cite tweet|user=Lin_Manuel|last=Miranda|first=Lin-Manuel|number=1250415048918532096|title=Can’t wait to keep making #TickTickBoomMovie. Must wait. Our last night of filming before the shutdown, recreating 508 Greenwich, Jon’s address, circa 1990|date=2020-04-15|accessdate=2020-10-21}}</ref>。復拍於同年10月開始進行，並於11月[[殺青|殺青]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Andrew Garfield Filming New Movie in New York Debunks Spider-Man 3 Rumors|url=http://epicstream.com/news/BriConstantino/Andrew-Garfield-Filming-New-Movie-in-New-York-Debunks-Spider-Man-3-Rumors|access-date=2020-10-24|website=epicstream.com|archive-date=2021-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211119214823/https://epicstream.com/article/andrew-garfield-filming-new-movie-in-new-york-debunks-spider-man-3-rumors|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.playbill.com/article/in-the-news-tick-tickboom-movie-wraps-filming-a-sneak-peek-at-matthew-morrisons-grinch-more|title=In the News: Tick, Tick...BOOM! Movie Wraps Filming, a Sneak Peek at Matthew Morrison's Grinch, More|publisher=Playbill|date=2020-11-30|accessdate=2021-01-13|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201010042/https://www.playbill.com/article/in-the-news-tick-tickboom-movie-wraps-filming-a-sneak-peek-at-matthew-morrisons-grinch-more|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《倒數時刻》定於2021年11月10日在[[美國電影學會|AFI Fest]]首映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2021/08/lin-manuel-mirandas-tick-tick-boom-afi-fest-opening-1234812952/|title=Lin-Manuel Miranda’s Feature Directorial Debut ‘tick, tick…BOOM!’ Set As Opening Night Film For AFI Fest November 10|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Pete|last=Hammond|date=2021-08-11|access-date=2021-08-11|archive-date=2021-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811180147/https://deadline.com/2021/08/lin-manuel-mirandas-tick-tick-boom-afi-fest-opening-1234812952/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於2021年11月12日在美國[[有限上映|有限上映]]，2021年11月19日在[[Netflix|Netflix]]上線<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/lin-manuel-miranda-tick-tick-boom-afi-fest-1235039419/|title=Lin-Manuel Miranda’s ‘Tick, Tick…Boom!’ to Open AFI Fest|website=Variety|first=Angelique|last=Jackson|date=2021-08-11|access-date=2021-08-11|archive-date=2021-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811180334/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/lin-manuel-miranda-tick-tick-boom-afi-fest-1235039419/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

